# Ticket Email Allowed Domains

**Rule**: Only ticket emails from Gmail, Yahoo, and Hotmail create tickets or complaints from inbound email.

## Implementation

- **Config**: `config/tickets.php` → `auto_ticket_from_email.allowed_sender_domains`
- **Env**: `TICKET_EMAIL_ALLOWED_DOMAINS` (comma-separated, default: gmail.com, googlemail.com, yahoo.com, yahoo.co.ke, yahoo.co.uk, ymail.com, rocketmail.com, hotmail.com, hotmail.co.ke, hotmail.co.uk, live.com, outlook.com, outlook.co.ke, msn.com)
- **Services**: `AutoTicketFromEmailService`, `AutoComplaintFromEmailService` (when added) check `isAllowedSenderDomain()` before creating records
- **Override**: Set `TICKET_EMAIL_ALLOWED_DOMAINS=` (empty) to allow all domains (except excluded)
